 the discretion of the hotel, the credit card provided may be charged if the reservation is canceled after the cancellation deadline has passed or if the guest fails to arrive. The cancellation policy will appear after selecting rate rules. Please wait. Loading ...    Areas Served LaGuardia Airport LGA 12 mi, Kennedy Int'l Airport JFK 15 mi, Radio City Music Hall 0.25 mi, Theater District 0.25 mi, Fifth Avenue 0.25 mi, Central Park 0.5 mi, Rockefeller Center 0.25 mi   Nearby Attractions The hotel's own Fitness Centre features a good range of cardiovascular equipment and weights, and guests may take advantage of the Equitable Health and Swim Club which is situated across the street and offers world-class facilities for a nominal charge.     Restaurants Restaurants - Insieme: Featuring traditional Italian classics and techniques deeply-rooted in history as well as a modern take on Italian cuisine. The quiet strength of each ingredient in the palette evokes an ancient Italian past with an unabashedly modern vocabulary. The 75-seat restaurant, designed by award-winning architects Bentel & Bentel, is warm and intimate, featuring natural materials such as weathered white oak, cork and travertine. A 30-seat private dining room downstairs is fashioned to resemble a wine barrel, with cork walls and lush burgundy carpeting. Insieme is open for Breakfast,Lunch and Dinner.   The Michelangelo Hotel - Traveler Reviews Read all hotel reviews Contact our 24/7 Customer Service Center New reservations: Please call 1-888-254-0637 Outside the US please call 1-210-507-5997 Give code 15701 when calling Existing reservations: Contact a Customer Service representative at 866-270-2849 Book Online or By Phone Select check-in date Select check-out date home car rental flights travel insurance group bookingstickets and attractions advertise | contact us | site map | about us | privacy policy | Review / Cancell Reservation | terms & conditions Book online or call: 1-888-254-0637 USA and Canada 